com.isbx.androidtools.networking.s3

Class S3Credentials

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.isbx.androidtools.networking.s3.S3Credentials

  • public class S3Credentials
extends Object
    This class contains all of the credential information necessary to make an authenticated upload request to an Amazon S3 bucket. Generally an instance of this class will be returned by an S3CredentialsProvider which handles the actual authentication process and populates this class with the appropriate information.
    See Also:
    S3CredentialsProvider

        public String getPolicy()

        Returns:

        public void setSignature(String signature)
